title: Remote Viewing - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 8/25/22
itunes:title: Remote Viewing - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 8/25/22
description:
George Noory and retired Army Major Ed Dames discuss his long career as an intelligence officer involved in remote viewing, his efforts helping law enforcement solve crimes, as well as his predictions of military conflicts with Russia and China.
